{"id": "art-1536", "label": "Art. 1536", "title": "Art. 1536", "slug": "art-1536", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_988413060\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2115\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_988413060\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>6</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_327467515\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2114\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_327467515\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Membrii consiliului de supraveghere sunt <span\nclass=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span> de c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span>\nprimilor membri, care sunt <span class=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span> prin actul\nconstitutiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_776913905\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2113\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_776913905\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Candida&#355;ii</span> pentru\nposturile de membru în consiliul de supraveghere sunt <span class=SpellE>nominaliza&#355;i</span>\nde c&#259;tre membrii <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;i</span> ai consiliului\nsau de c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1585483713\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2112\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1585483713\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Num&#259;rul membrilor consiliului de supraveghere este\nstabilit prin actul constitutiv. Acesta nu poate fi mai mic de 3 <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nici mai mare de 11.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_556979635\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2111\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_556979635\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Membrii consiliului de supraveghere pot fi <span\nclass=SpellE>revoca&#355;i</span> oricând de adunarea general&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, cu o majoritate de cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> dou&#259; treimi din num&#259;rul voturilor <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1079817181\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2110\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1079817181\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Consiliul de supraveghere alege dintre membrii s&#259;i\nun <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edinte</span> al consiliului.</span></p>"}